Hi,

I would like to announce the enhanced ocaml documentation 
version 3.00 available via
http://wwwtcs.inf.tu-dresden.de/~tews/software.html.

The enhanced documentation contains in
http://wwwtcs.inf.tu-dresden.de/~tews/htmlman-3.00/ the original
html version of the ocaml reference manual with the following
changes:

- Changes (wrt version 2.04) are tagged with icons and color

- meta symbols of the grammar are "hot" and refer to their
  definition. 

There is also a page
http://wwwtcs.inf.tu-dresden.de/~tews/htmlman-3.00/full-grammar.html
containing all grammar rules from the reference manual for easy
and quick reference.

Bye,

Hendrik

